<title>USA: National Media names new CEO.</title>
<headline>National Media names new CEO.</headline>
<dateline>PHILADELPHIA 1997-04-28</dateline>
<text>
<p>National Media Corp said that it had appointed Robert Verratti as president and chief executive to replace Mark Hershhorn, who has resgined.</p>
<p>National Media said in a statement on Monday that the parting was amicable and was &quot;the result of the recognition by Hershhorn and the board of directors that their approaches to the development of the company's business differed significantly.&quot;</p>
<p>Before joining National Media, Verratti was a special advisor for acquisitions to Warren Musser, the chief executive of Safeguard Scientifics Inc. ((--New York Newsroom 212 859 1902))</p>
